928
00:59:58,659 --> 01:00:00,697
JORGE: It does look kind of like Buddy.

929
01:00:00,785 --> 01:00:03,785
FENTON: I think he'll run
that Mexican kid in for loitering.

930
01:00:03,870 --> 01:00:05,862
SAM: Nice to see you, Mrs. Cruz.

931
01:00:17,335 --> 01:00:18,828
Field trip?

932
01:00:19,002 --> 01:00:20,330
Lunch hour.

933
01:00:20,503 --> 01:00:22,827
My next class isn't until 1:30.

934
01:00:25,296 --> 01:00:27,004
You want to take a walk?

935
01:00:39,679 --> 01:00:42,796
They cooked the whole thing up
without asking me.

936
01:00:43,097 --> 01:00:44,839
People liked him.

937
01:00:47,015 --> 01:00:48,841
Most people did, yeah.

938
01:00:52,142 --> 01:00:54,467
I remember him watching me once...

939
01:00:55,228 --> 01:00:56,851
...when I was little...

940
01:00:57,104 --> 01:00:58,680
...before you and I....

941
01:01:02,022 --> 01:01:05,140
I was in the playground
with all the other kids.

942
01:01:05,816 --> 01:01:08,187
I thought he was only looking at me.

943
01:01:09,359 --> 01:01:12,063
I was afraid he was going to arrest me.

944
01:01:12,194 --> 01:01:14,315
He had those eyes, and that....

945
01:01:14,528 --> 01:01:15,642
Yeah.

946
01:01:17,446 --> 01:01:19,687
It's weird what you remember.

947
01:01:24,992 --> 01:01:26,319
Your boy there.

948
01:01:27,326 --> 01:01:28,155
Amado.

949
01:01:28,243 --> 01:01:29,356
Nice looking kid.

950
01:01:29,451 --> 01:01:30,614
He hates me.

951
01:01:32,745 --> 01:01:33,693
No.

952
01:01:34,954 --> 01:01:39,828
With Paloma, it's like she pities
and tolerates me, totally age-appropriate.

953
01:01:40,207 --> 01:01:41,831
But with Amado...

954
01:01:42,333 --> 01:01:46,328
...you know, he's always had
difficulty reading and me...

955
01:01:46,668 --> 01:01:51,542
...being a teacher and caring
about those things, it's like a betrayal.

956
01:01:51,629 --> 01:01:53,372
But Fernando did okay.

957
01:01:53,505 --> 01:01:54,832
He dropped out.

958
01:01:54,922 --> 01:01:59,498
Fernando wasn't pissed off at everybody.
He just wanted to fix their cars.

959
01:02:01,842 --> 01:02:05,458
I spent my first 15 years
trying to be just like Buddy.

960
01:02:05,885 --> 01:02:08,720
The next 15 trying
to give him a heart attack.

961
01:02:16,515 --> 01:02:19,005
So, why did you come back here, Sam?

962
01:02:22,560 --> 01:02:24,183
I got divorced...

963
01:02:27,062 --> 01:02:30,061
...and I wouldn't work
for my father-in-law anymore.

964
01:02:31,315 --> 01:02:33,390
<i>And the fellas down here...

965
01:02:34,274 --> 01:02:36,265
<i>...they said they'd back me.

966
01:02:37,734 --> 01:02:39,642
You don't want to be sheriff.

967
01:02:41,861 --> 01:02:44,565
I got to admit,
it's not what I thought it'd be.

968
01:02:45,529 --> 01:02:47,568
Back when Buddy had it....

969
01:02:51,949 --> 01:02:53,941
Hell, I'm just a jailer.

970
01:02:55,701 --> 01:02:58,902
Run a 60-room hotel
with bars on the windows.

971
01:03:03,288 --> 01:03:04,781
Do you remember this?

972
01:03:08,915 --> 01:03:10,741
I ought to head back.

973
01:03:11,625 --> 01:03:14,743
It looks real bad
if a teacher's late for class.

974
01:03:17,336 --> 01:03:19,873
It's real nice to talk with you, Sam.

975
01:03:50,185 --> 01:03:51,892
SAM: Are you going to tell her?

976
01:03:54,354 --> 01:03:55,847
Are you going to tell him?

977
01:03:55,938 --> 01:03:57,810
He doesn't need to know my business.

978
01:03:58,688 --> 01:04:00,479
He's going to find out.

979
01:04:00,689 --> 01:04:02,811
What is he going to do, arrest us?

980
01:04:06,025 --> 01:04:09,523
It's supposed to be a big sin
even if you love each other.

981
01:04:11,028 --> 01:04:12,521
Do you believe that?

982
01:04:14,363 --> 01:04:15,441
No.

983
01:04:36,368 --> 01:04:37,613
Me neither.

984
01:04:41,662 --> 01:04:43,156
PRISCILLA: Private Johnson!

985
01:04:45,081 --> 01:04:47,287
Report to the sergeant
in the orderly's room.

986
01:04:47,373 --> 01:04:49,199
The doctor will have a look at you.

987
01:04:49,291 --> 01:04:50,833
No, I'm feeling okay.

988
01:04:51,375 --> 01:04:52,620
I'm happy to hear it.

989
01:04:52,710 --> 01:04:56,575
You go put some pee-pee in the cup
