01:17:25,688 --> 01:17:27,017
What's in the back?

1123
01:17:27,106 --> 01:17:29,726
Not much,<i>jefe</i>. Some watermelons.

1124
01:17:30,274 --> 01:17:32,313
ELADIO: I'm driving them up to the market.

1125
01:17:32,400 --> 01:17:34,356
ELADIO: They could bring a good price.

1126
01:17:37,819 --> 01:17:40,818
WADE: I heard somebody's been
hauling wets on this road.

1127
01:17:42,280 --> 01:17:44,520
I haven't seen anybody doing that.

1128
01:17:46,115 --> 01:17:48,569
That person's been bragging
all over the county...

1129
01:17:48,658 --> 01:17:52,071
...how he doesn't have to cut
that gringo sheriff in on it.

1130
01:17:52,201 --> 01:17:54,572
Run his own operation without any help.

1131
01:17:56,119 --> 01:17:57,448
[In Spanish ] <i>What's your name?

1132
01:17:58,120 --> 01:17:59,400
Eladio Cruz.

1133
01:18:01,413 --> 01:18:04,366
You know this road's got a bad reputation.

1134
01:18:04,999 --> 01:18:06,243
Reputation?

1135
01:18:06,416 --> 01:18:08,075
<i>Bandidos</i>, Injuns.

1136
01:18:09,417 --> 01:18:13,164
Many an unfortunate soul
has been ambushed out on this stretch.

1137
01:18:13,252 --> 01:18:15,577
I hope you're carrying some protection.

1138
01:18:15,796 --> 01:18:17,075
Protection?

1139
01:18:18,296 --> 01:18:20,418
You carrying a firearm, son?

1140
01:18:20,881 --> 01:18:22,291
Don't lie to me now.

1141
01:18:25,467 --> 01:18:26,581
Just a shotgun.

1142
01:18:27,593 --> 01:18:28,837
Just a shotgun.

1143
01:18:29,552 --> 01:18:31,590
Then let me have a look at that.

1144
01:18:42,016 --> 01:18:43,130
[Gasps]

1145
01:18:45,101 --> 01:18:48,515
Little greaser son of a bitch is running
a goddamn bus service.

1146
01:18:48,602 --> 01:18:51,223
Thinks he can make a fool
out of Charlie Wade.

1147
01:18:51,604 --> 01:18:53,643
Get them wets out of the back.

1148
01:18:53,730 --> 01:18:55,188
See what we've got.

1149
01:18:59,733 --> 01:19:01,227
HOLLIS: You killed him!

1150
